{"tid":1633621,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今晚開花去貼文宣啦","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:17:32.000Z","uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"263ba408bc42a6a8de4aabfbf91d3c329a570a6d","tid":1633621,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都冇做文宣"},{"pid":"af1e9e4abd6017648ea4351b744a6049a1f5b290","tid":1633621,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:40:25.000Z","msg":"有時唔洗下下硬打既，轉個方式抗爭都得<br />\n比勇武叉叉電 比文宣組做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},{"pid":"42226bade0470fed7e5a8fe5fdb3c185b9a3fb35","tid":1633621,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:45:33.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但黨鐵而家咁撚樣你都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e0aba36925690381d19c6ef83160aee495e2bd","tid":1633621,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26f3fb7a96abe48e52da93537c74c1e68a89ddf1","tid":1633621,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8bb840cd054c1fff3bb2f09c7b0065df67d872","tid":1633621,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05fe29499b681b8f033